<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt 36pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; text-indent: -18pt;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;">4.<span style="font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style="font-size: 14pt;">Every day we wish we were there, Oh&nbsp;<span class="SpellE">Hussain</span>&nbsp;(as) right by your side</span></p>
<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;">We would have stood to protect you, and for you we would have died</span></p>
<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;">Everything we have in your name, happily we&rsquo;d sacrifice</span></p>
<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;">You would not need to convince us, or need to even ask us twice</span></p>
<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;">As we breathe our final breath for, you our love we would proclaim</span></p>
<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;">If you stop our lips from moving, through our blood we&rsquo;ll write&nbsp;<span class="SpellE">Hussain</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;">You can bomb us, shoot us, kill us, but we&rsquo;ll never feel the pain</span></p>
<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;">If you stop our lips from moving, through our blood we&rsquo;ll write&nbsp;<span class="SpellE">Hussain</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt 36pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; text-indent: -18pt;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;">5.<span style="font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style="font-size: 14pt;">We are crying for that martyr who was stranded all alone</span></p>
<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;">He was shrouded by the&nbsp;<span class="GramE">arrows,</span>&nbsp;he was wounded by the stones</span></p>
<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;">Then the enemy began to cut his neck right to the bone</span></p>
<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;">As the heartbeats ebbed away his, name in history was sewn</span></p>
<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;">&lsquo;<span class="SpellE">Pon</span>&nbsp;remembering this image, our grief&nbsp;<span class="GramE">cant</span>&nbsp;be contained</span></p>
