<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;">And the prophet then consoled her, as he wiped the tears he vowed</span></p>
