<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt 36pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; text-indent: -18pt;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;">7.<span style="font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style="font-size: 14pt;">When we listen to your story, the Tejani brothers cry</span></p>
<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;">Our heart is cut to pieces, but we know that every night</span></p>
<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;">Our Imam&nbsp;<span class="SpellE">Mehdi</span>&nbsp;is crying, blood is pouring from his eyes</span></p>
