<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;">His words won&rsquo;t shake me</span></p>
<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;">When you will awake me</span></p>
<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;">Your light will save me</span></p>
<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;">The evil will hate me</span></p>
