                'text' => '<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><strong><u><span style="font-size: 14pt;"><a style="color: purple;" href="http://www.nawhas.com/sa13/06.mp3">Breaths Whisper audio</a></span></u></strong></p>
<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><strong><u><span style="font-size: 14pt;"><a style="color: purple;" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SqTYiPrdd-Q">Breaths Whisper lyrics video</a></span></u></strong></p>
<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><strong><u><span style="font-size: 14pt;">Breaths Whisper</span></u></strong></p>
<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span class="SpellE"><span style="font-size: 14pt;">Hussain</span></span><span style="font-size: 14pt;">&nbsp;you are my guide, in my hour of need</span></p>
<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;">When I am all alone, and there&rsquo;s no-one with me</span></p>
<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;">Submerged in darkness,&nbsp;<span class="SpellE"><span class="GramE">its</span></span>&nbsp;all that&nbsp;<span class="SpellE">i</span>&nbsp;see</span></p>
<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;">When I will search for you, I know that I&rsquo;ll be free</span></p>
<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span class="SpellE"><span style="font-size: 14pt;">Hussain</span></span><span style="font-size: 14pt;">&nbsp;you are the light, inside my darkest night</span></p>
<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span class="SpellE"><span style="font-size: 14pt;">Hussain</span></span><span style="font-size: 14pt;">&nbsp;you&rsquo;ve made me whole,</span></p>
<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;">Through you I&rsquo;ve found my soul</span></p>
<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;">And&nbsp;<span class="SpellE">everyday</span>&nbsp;I say&nbsp;<span class="SpellE">Ya</span>&nbsp;<span class="SpellE">Hussain</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;">Your body was lying there, without a shroud</span></p>
<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;">Completely ravaged making no sound</span></p>
<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;">The enemies watched, standing so proud</span></p>
<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;">As Lady&nbsp;<span class="SpellE">Zainab</span>&nbsp;cried out aloud</span></p>
<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span class="SpellE"><span style="font-size: 14pt;">Hussain</span></span><span style="font-size: 14pt;">&nbsp;you are the light, inside my darkest night</span></p>
<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span class="SpellE"><span style="font-size: 14pt;">Hussain</span></span><span style="font-size: 14pt;">&nbsp;you&rsquo;ve made me whole,</span></p>
<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span class="GramE"><span style="font-size: 14pt;">through</span></span><span style="font-size: 14pt;">&nbsp;you I&rsquo;ve found my soul</span></p>
<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;">And&nbsp;<span class="SpellE">everyday</span>&nbsp;I say&nbsp;<span class="SpellE">Ya</span>&nbsp;<span class="SpellE">Hussain</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;">(<span class="SpellE">Ya</span>&nbsp;<span class="SpellE">Hussain</span>,&nbsp;<span class="SpellE">Ya</span>&nbsp;<span class="SpellE">Hussain</span>) x2</span></p>
<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;">You taught us the art of dying,&nbsp;<span class="GramE">And</span>&nbsp;giving others life</span></p>
<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;">By being that light that&rsquo;s shining,&nbsp;<span class="GramE">In</span>&nbsp;the darkest of the nights</span></p>
<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;">You showed us the way of giving,&nbsp;<span class="GramE">The</span>&nbsp;ultimate sacrifice</span></p>
<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;">Stand for what you believe in, even if you have to die</span></p>
<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;">When I have got no hope, I remember your day</span></p>
<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;">When I feel like I can&rsquo;t cope, I think of your pain</span></p>
<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;">When life can&rsquo;t go on,&nbsp;<span class="GramE">My</span>&nbsp;heart beats your name</span></p>
<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;">When I&rsquo;ve lost it all,&nbsp;<span class="GramE">My</span>&nbsp;breaths whisper&nbsp;<span class="SpellE">Hussain</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;">Breaths whisper&nbsp;<span class="SpellE">Hussain</span></span></p>
