                'text' => '<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><strong><u><span style="font-size: 14pt;"><a style="color: purple;" href="http://www.nawhas.com/sa1011/3.mp3">Abbas Ho Kahaan audio file</a></span></u></strong></p>
<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><strong><u><span style="font-size: 14pt;">Abbas Ho Kahaan</span></u></strong></p>
<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;">(Mere Abbas ho kahaa(n)) x2</span></p>
<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;">Abbas ho kahaa(n), mere Abbas ho kahaa(n)</span></p>
<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;">Bemakhna aur be chadar</span></p>
<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;">Kehti hai bibi Zainab rokar</span></p>
<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;">Ay sheyr-e-karwaa(n)</span></p>
<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;">(Aal-e-nabi aur sham ka rasta, Koi nahi zainab ka sahara, Abbas ho kahaa(n)) x2</span></p>
<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;">Sharm ye ati hai mujhko ke, sar pe nahi koi bhi parda</span></p>
<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;">Sharm ki had hai ye ghazi ke, dekh rahe ho tum ay bhayya</span></p>
<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;">Kaise karu(n) baalo(n) ki chadar</span></p>
<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;">Khaak-e-shifa ko sar pe rakh kar</span></p>
<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;">Ab hu(n) mei yak-zabaa(n)</span></p>
<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;">Mere abbas ho kahaa(n)</span></p>
<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;">(Aal-e-nabi aur sham ka rasta, Koi nahi zainab ka sahara, Abbas ho kahaa(n)) x2</span></p>
<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;">Gham se bhara hai qalb ye mera, Sham ke is darbaar ke andar</span></p>
<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;">Tasht tille pe bhayi ka sar hai, nok-e-sina par tu ay dilawar</span></p>
<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;">Zakhm hazaro(n) hai ye dil mei(n)</span></p>
<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;">Mei hu(n) anbaar-e-qatil mei(n)</span></p>
<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;">Hu aayina-e-maa(n)</span></p>
<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;">Mere abbas ho kahaa(n)</span></p>
<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;">(Aal-e-nabi aur sham ka rasta, Koi nahi zainab ka sahara, Abbas ho kahaa(n)) x2</span></p>
<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;">Ponch gaye shiree(n) ke gar pe, pooch rahi hai wo hasrat se</span></p>
<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;">Saath mei aye hai kya maula, ayi hai Zainab kya ghurbat se</span></p>
<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;">Boli ke haaye mei hu(n) Zainab,</span></p>
<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;">Aal-e-muhammad ke bete sab,</span></p>
<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;">Neze pe hai(n) yahaa(n)</span></p>
