<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';"><span lang="EN-GB" style="font-size: 14pt;">(Haaye Zainab, haaye Zainab) x2</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';"><span lang="EN-GB" style="font-size: 14pt;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';"><em><span lang="EN-GB" style="font-size: 14pt;">Issi Hussain ko roya hai umr bhar Sajjad</span></em></p>
