<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';"><em><span lang="EN-GB" style="font-size: 14pt;">Issi Hussain ki khaahar hai Zainab-e-nashaad</span></em></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';"><em><span style="font-size: 14pt;">Likha hai jiski rida par Hussain Zindabad</span></em></p>
