<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';"><em><span lang="EN-GB" style="font-size: 14pt;">Ye zindagi hai uski nikaali huwi zakaat</span></em></p>
