<p style="margin-right: 0cm; margin-left: 36pt; font-size: medium; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt;">Dard ye puchhe koi hazrate shabbir se</span></p>
<p style="margin-right: 0cm; margin-left: 36pt; font-size: medium; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt;">Surkh tha ujla kafan aap ka jab teer se</span></p>
<p style="margin-right: 0cm; margin-left: 36pt; font-size: medium; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt;">Ay ruh-e-mustafa, Ay ibn-e-murtaza, ay jaan-e-sayyeda</span></p>
