<p style="margin-right: 0cm; margin-left: 36pt; font-size: medium; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt;">Kayse sitamghar the baniye zulmo jafa</span></p>
<p style="margin-right: 0cm; margin-left: 36pt; font-size: medium; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt;">Kayse laeeno ne ki zulm ki ye inteha</span></p>
