                'id' => 85,
                'text' => '<p style="font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: medium;"><a href="http://www.nawhas.com/sa2008/sayyeda%20fatemah.ram"><strong>Sayyada Fatemah audio file</strong></a></p>
<p>Sayyada Fatemah</p>
<p style="font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: medium;"><span style="font-size: large;">(Sayada fatemah) x12</span></p>
<ol>
<ol>
<li>Shohar wali, pidar hai payambar, pisar imam</li>
</ol>
</ol>
<p>Jis bibi ka nabi pe, lazim tha ehtaraam</p>
<p>Ummat ko baad-e-ehmad, ayi na kyu(n) haya</p>
<p>(Sayyada fatemah) x8</p>
<ol>
<ol>
<li>Duniya ko khalq karke, Allah ne kaha,</li>
</ol>
</ol>
<p>Sara jahaan tere, sadqe me hai bana</p>
<p>Uncha hai kitna bibi, ye martaba tera</p>
<p>(Sayyada fatemah) x8</p>
<ol>
<ol>
<li>Bibi tumhare dar se humko hai aasra</li>
</ol>
</ol>
<p>Zainab ka waasta hay sunlijiye dua</p>
<p>Miljaye roze hashr, chadar ki bas hawa</p>
<p>(Sayyada fatemah) x8</p>
<ol>
<ol>
<li>Kehti rahi mei fatema, bint-e-rasool hu(n)</li>
</ol>
</ol>
<p>Bagh-e-Fidak ko cheen ke khush ho rahe ho kyun</p>
<p>Bint-e-rasool ki hai, kya hai yahi jaza</p>
<p>(Sayyada fatemah) x8</p>
<ol>
<ol>
<li>Tutti huwi kamar hai, mohsin guzar gaye</li>
</ol>
</ol>
<p>Ummat ne mujh pe baba kya kya sitam kiye</p>
<p>Qabre rasool par yu(n) karti rahi buka</p>
<p>(Sayyada fatemah) x8</p>
<ol>
<ol>
<li>Zainab ko ye wasiyyat deti hai fatema</li>
</ol>
</ol>
<p>Bazar-e-sham o kufa ka hoga marhala,</p>
<p>Deene khuda ka us dam, tum hogi aasra</p>
<p>(Sayyada fatemah) x8</p>
<ol>
<ol>
<li>Zahra ka laal tha aur, zalim ki fauj thi</li>
</ol>
</ol>
<p>Chaaro(n) taraf se aayi, barsaat teer ki,</p>
<p>Gore se jab gire to, sarwar ne di sada</p>
<p>(Sayyada fatemah) x8</p>
<ol>
<ol>
<li>Balo(n) se saaf karti, zahra woh sar zami(n)</li>
</ol>
</ol>
<p>Jis khaak pe ghiregi, shabbir ki jabi(n)</p>
<p>Kya maa ke dil pe ghuzri, jab sheh ka sar kataa</p>
<p>(Sayyada fatemah) x8</p>
<ol>
<ol>
<li>Beparda qafla jab, aale rasul ka,</li>
</ol>
</ol>
<p>Karbobala me lut ke, zindan ko chala</p>
<p>Zainab ko har qadam par, deti thi hosla</p>
<p>(Sayyada fatemah) x8</p>
<ol>
<li>"Shabbir ki dua hai" Abbas ki dua</li>
</ol>
<p>Jeeteji nawha dono, parhte rahe tera</p>
<p>Marte huwe bhi lab par, bas ho yahi sadaa</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>(Sayyada fatemah) x8</p>',
